snippet.title: Mass Effect 3 VGA 2011 trailer
snippet.description: Very nice ME3 trailer. It's good to see Reaper getting it's ass kicked. Thanks to GameTrailers for uploading this video to their network! All credit for this trailer goes to Bioware and GameTrailers!
